            <bug_when>2010-01-15 17:07:49 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>Since rev. qooxdoo has native JSON support in qx.lang.Json. Since the old implementation extends JSON to support dates we cannot simply deprecate it and use the new one instead. The new implementation does not have this extension and it is not planned to add it.

Within the framework only the JSON-RPC code relies on date support. We have to find a way to support dates in JSON_RPC in a JSON compatible way.</thetext>
